com.indragie.cmput301as1

Class TypedObservable<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.indragie.cmput301as1.TypedObservable<T>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ExpenseClaimDetailModel, ExpenseClaimListController, ListModel

    public class TypedObservable<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents an observable object that can have one or more observers that implement the interface TypedObserver. After an observable instance changes, calling the #notifyObservers(T) method causes observers to be notified of the change via a call to their #TypedObserver.update(TypedObservable, T) method. This class is the same as Observable, except that the observers are typed.
